hivis.data.view

Class AbstractValueView<I,O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hivis.data.DataDefault
      • hivis.data.AbstractDataValue<V>
        • hivis.data.AbstractUnmodifiableDataValue<O>
          • hivis.data.view.AbstractValueView<I,O>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Data, DataListener, DataValue<O>, Comparable<O>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CalcValue

    public abstract class AbstractValueView<I,O>
extends AbstractUnmodifiableDataValue<O>
implements DataListener
    Base class for creating DataValues that are optionally based on one or more other DataValues or DataSeries. If input DataValues or DataSeries are provided then change events on those DataValues or DataSeries are forwarded to this DataValue.
    Author:
    O. J. Coleman
